00:53:43,486 --> 00:53:44,321
- Oh my God!

800
00:53:44,321 --> 00:53:45,288
Julie!

801
00:53:45,289 --> 00:53:50,293
Julie!

802
00:54:01,438 --> 00:54:05,007
(music intensifies)

803
00:54:05,008 --> 00:54:07,409
(choking)

804
00:54:07,410 --> 00:54:09,646
(grunting)

805
00:54:20,690 --> 00:54:23,759
