808
00:54:32,836 --> 00:54:35,105
(grunting)

809
00:54:36,506 --> 00:54:38,107
(gunshot)

810
00:54:38,108 --> 00:54:40,844
(Jason groaning)

811
00:54:49,653 --> 00:54:50,487
- I guess I can't find here

812
00:54:50,488 --> 00:54:53,255
everything I was looking for, huh?

813
00:54:53,256 --> 00:54:55,425
(gunshot)

814
00:55:03,867 --> 00:55:05,801
- Well, now we can be together.

815
00:55:05,802 --> 00:55:07,102
I mean everything that
was in our way before

816
00:55:07,103 --> 00:55:08,103
