00:55:24,321 --> 00:55:25,321
- Why?

822
00:55:26,189 --> 00:55:27,923
So we can be together.

823
00:55:27,924 --> 00:55:29,425
Just like it was meant to be.

824
00:55:29,426 --> 00:55:30,526
Because I love you.

825
00:55:30,527 --> 00:55:31,660
- You're crazy.

826
00:55:31,661 --> 00:55:33,262
- Crazy?

827
00:55:33,263 --> 00:55:34,264
Crazy for you.

828
00:55:36,566 --> 00:55:38,267
Crazy cause I love you.

829
00:55:38,268 --> 00:55:39,802
