831
00:55:40,737 --> 00:55:41,705
You make me sick!

832
00:55:41,706 --> 00:55:43,639
- Hey, don't say such silly things!

833
00:55:43,640 --> 00:55:45,140
- Help me!

834
00:55:45,141 --> 00:55:46,141
- Shut up.

835
00:55:46,142 --> 00:55:48,010
Shut the fuck up, you stupid bitch.

836
00:55:48,011 --> 00:55:49,611
