837
00:55:49,612 --> 00:55:52,214
No, you can't see it. You want Rick.

838
00:55:52,215 --> 00:55:54,249
Just like Mary wanted Peter.

839
00:55:54,250 --> 00:55:56,052
Just like Cara wanted Chris.

840
00:55:57,354 --> 00:55:58,722
You want Rick over me, huh?

841
00:56:00,490 --> 00:56:01,623
Well, it's a good thing.

842
00:56:01,624 --> 00:56:02,891
Tell you what,

843
00:56:02,892 --> 00:56:04,460
I'll take you to him now.

844
00:56:04,461 --> 00:56:05,495
Aw, don't cry.

845
00:56:06,329 --> 00:56:09,465
Close your eyes and say good night.

846
00:56:09,466 --> 00:56:12,735
Because it's the last thing
you'll ever say in this world.

847
00:56:12,736 --> 00:56:13,670
